rtservice->redis\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"paymentservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"支付服务完全不可用：checkoutservice调用paymentservice的Charge操作出现严重延迟，从正常13.8秒激增至2275万秒，延迟倍数达1640倍，错误状态为'connection error: dial tcp 10.233.55.4:50051: i/o timeout'\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\", \n      \"evidence\": \"结账服务受支付服务故障影响：PlaceOrder操作延迟从正常155秒增至2285万秒，延迟倍数147倍，大量HTTP 500错误和context canceled错误\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"前端服务作为受害者：接收用户请求时出现HTTP 500错误，受下游checkoutservice故障影响\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"运输服务延迟增加：GetQuote操作从正常9.4秒增至38.3秒，延迟倍数4倍\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"emailservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\", \n      \"evidence\": \"邮件服务延迟增加：SendOrderConfirmation操作从正常24.5秒增至77.2秒，延迟倍数3.1倍\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 关键发现总结：\n\n**根因定位**：`paymentservice`（支付服务）是本次故障的根本原因，其完全不可用导致整个订单处理链路中断。\n\n**故障传播路径**：\n1. `paymentservice` → 连接超时和I/O超时错误\n2. `checkoutservice` → 支付失败导致订单处理失败\n3. `frontend` → 用户请求返回HTTP 500错误\n\n**延迟分析**：\n- 支付服务延迟激增1640倍，表明服务完全不可用\n- 结账服务延迟增加147倍，为受害者\n- 其他相关服务（运输、邮件）也有3-4倍的延迟增加\n\n**错误类型**：主要是连接超时和I/O超时错误，表明支付服务网络连接或服务本身出现问题。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nNo consensus yet\n\n--- Metric Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Trace Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nAGREED", "log_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "metric_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "trace_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "report_analysis_findings": {"uuid": "92e5a649-207", "component": "paymentservice", "reason": "transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.55.4:50051: i/o timeout causing complete service u